1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:40,970
[Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty II To the West]

3
00:01:41,550 --> 00:01:43,920
[Episode 39]

4
00:01:45,020 --> 00:01:47,850
[Government Office of Shazhou]

5
00:01:51,860 --> 00:01:53,830
Guys, as you expected,

6
00:01:54,030 --> 00:01:55,550
after I used some tricks,

7
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:57,140
the patriarch of the Cao family

8
00:01:57,140 --> 00:01:59,190
and Red Robe, Green Robe, and Blue Robe,

9
00:01:59,190 --> 00:02:00,430
the three so-called supervisors

10
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:02,070
of the Supervisory Committee,

11
00:02:02,070 --> 00:02:03,270
all confessed.

12
00:02:04,550 --> 00:02:06,790
Please tell us the details.

13
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:08,110
The patriarch

14
00:02:08,620 --> 00:02:10,410
was down and out.

15
00:02:11,070 --> 00:02:12,000
Half a month ago,

16
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:13,470
Cao Xiao

17
00:02:13,990 --> 00:02:14,950
went to him.

18
00:02:16,390 --> 00:02:16,910
Sir,

19
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:18,520
today,

20
00:02:19,110 --> 00:02:20,170
I'm here to beg you.

21
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:22,980
The 60th birthday funeral of Zhongda is approaching.

22
00:02:22,980 --> 00:02:24,590
If you want to beg me to make an exception,

23
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:25,950
say no more.

24
00:02:26,510 --> 00:02:28,510
This rule has existed for a few hundred years.

25
00:02:28,510 --> 00:02:29,510
We can't break it.

26
00:02:29,750 --> 00:02:32,010
I didn't come to you because of my father.

27
00:02:32,270 --> 00:02:33,270
Then what is it?

28
00:02:33,900 --> 00:02:35,190
Usually, when you met your elders,

29
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:35,870
you wouldn't even greet them.

30
00:02:35,870 --> 00:02:37,470
But now, you are here

31
00:02:37,490 --> 00:02:38,329
to beg me.

32
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:42,670
As you know,

33
00:02:42,950 --> 00:02:44,990
my family has a lot of properties.

34
00:02:45,230 --> 00:02:46,310
But we are

35
00:02:46,790 --> 00:02:48,050
really short-handed.

36
00:02:49,070 --> 00:02:51,730
We have a prosperous shop in the west of the city.

37
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,760
It's been rented by an outsider.

38
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:55,190
So the money earned naturally

39
00:02:55,190 --> 00:02:56,390
goes to the outsider.

40
00:02:56,750 --> 00:02:57,750
What a pity.

41
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:58,829
You are

42
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,690
in the prime of life.

43
00:03:01,230 --> 00:03:02,600
You are of good character

44
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:03,930
and have a wide network.

45
00:03:04,260 --> 00:03:07,550
If you run the shop,

46
00:03:08,100 --> 00:03:10,100
you can earn a lot of money every day.

47
00:03:10,710 --> 00:03:12,040
I can't afford the rent.

48
00:03:13,670 --> 00:03:15,000
Who asked you to rent it?

49
00:03:15,350 --> 00:03:16,280
I'll

50
00:03:16,790 --> 00:03:17,460
just...

51
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:19,040
give the shop to you.

52
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,470
What?

53
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,380
But you have to give 20%

54
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:24,680
of the profit you make to the pawnshop.

55
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:25,710
Your descendants

56
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:27,579
can inherit this business.

57
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:29,170
But they also have to give

58
00:03:29,170 --> 00:03:30,370
20% of the profit.

59
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:31,590
My conditions

60
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,780
are stringent enough, right?

61
00:03:34,300 --> 00:03:35,150
If so, I'll

62
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:36,270
take great advantage of your family.

63
00:03:36,270 --> 00:03:38,070
We both have a family name of Cao.

64
00:03:38,829 --> 00:03:39,670
We're one.

65
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:46,470
The money I borrowed from the pawnshop

66
00:03:46,470 --> 00:03:47,829
is not due yet.

67
00:03:47,990 --> 00:03:48,590
Xiao,

68
00:03:49,190 --> 00:03:52,710
you're not going to ask me to pay back the money in advance, are you?

69
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:53,910
Did you borrow money?

70
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:55,360
I don't think so.

71
00:03:55,829 --> 00:03:56,829
Here's the thing.

72
00:03:57,070 --> 00:03:59,190
A few days ago, the pawnshop caught fire.

73
00:03:59,190 --> 00:04:00,840
The ledger was burnt to ashes.

74
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,970
Without the ledger,

75
00:04:02,310 --> 00:04:03,310
I can't clearly remember

76
00:04:03,310 --> 00:04:04,510
the loans in the past.

77
00:04:04,950 --> 00:04:06,510
The shopkeeper told me

78
00:04:06,610 --> 00:04:08,510
the money you borrowed is about to be due.

79
00:04:08,510 --> 00:04:09,680
But I just couldn't

80
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:10,570
remember this.

81
00:04:11,350 --> 00:04:13,420
So I came to you to verify it.

82
00:04:19,740 --> 00:04:20,200
Well...

83
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:22,400
I don't deserve any reward.

84
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:24,600
You've always taken care of my family.

85
00:04:24,990 --> 00:04:26,800
Last year, the pawnshop didn't do well.

86
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,270
So we borrowed two gold coins from you.

87
00:04:28,270 --> 00:04:29,230
I'm really sorry

88
00:04:29,380 --> 00:04:30,910
that I didn't pay them back to you earlier.

89
00:04:30,910 --> 00:04:32,110
I invited you here today

90
00:04:32,110 --> 00:04:33,570
because I want

91
00:04:34,230 --> 00:04:35,560
to discuss the interest

92
00:04:35,790 --> 00:04:36,600
with you.

93
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:39,430
When did I lend gold coins to your family?

94
00:04:39,430 --> 00:04:40,830
You're very forgetful.

95
00:04:42,470 --> 00:04:44,190
You've helped us a lot.

96
00:04:44,710 --> 00:04:45,820
Let's just...

97
00:04:46,260 --> 00:04:48,120
forget about the interest, okay?

98
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,540
Then...

99
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:51,680
forget about it.

100
00:04:54,180 --> 00:04:56,540
[IOU]

101
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:55,190
Yes.

102
00:04:55,380 --> 00:04:57,030
I borrowed money from your pawnshop.

103
00:04:57,030 --> 00:04:58,430
The loan was due long ago.

104
00:04:58,870 --> 00:05:00,070
I'm grateful that Zhongda

105
00:05:00,070 --> 00:05:01,870
has never come to collect debts.

106
00:05:02,190 --> 00:05:02,870
Today,

107
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:03,990
since you are here...

108
00:05:03,990 --> 00:05:05,150
I'm here

109
00:05:05,790 --> 00:05:06,910
to solve

110
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:08,510
the problem with you.

111
00:05:09,990 --> 00:05:10,550
Yes.

112
00:05:11,230 --> 00:05:13,310
It's natural that I should pay off the debts.

113
00:05:13,310 --> 00:05:13,910
I admit it.

114
00:05:14,990 --> 00:05:16,590
Please give me ten more days.

115
00:05:17,790 --> 00:05:18,920
No. Not even one day.

116
00:05:19,670 --> 00:05:21,110
You've gone too far!

117
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:24,850
Well...

118
00:05:27,550 --> 00:05:28,880
Problem solved, right?

119
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:31,550
Sir,

120
00:05:32,550 --> 00:05:33,350
have some tea.

121
00:05:37,550 --> 00:05:38,550
Third Young Lady,

122
00:05:38,940 --> 00:05:40,110
a toast to you.

123
00:05:42,750 --> 00:05:44,040
These are the confessions.

124
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,840
The four of them all signed them.

125
00:05:46,750 --> 00:05:47,510
Cao Xiao

126
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:48,990
is young,

127
00:05:49,010 --> 00:05:50,220
but she's really something.

128
00:05:50,220 --> 00:05:52,080
The four of them all got benefits.

129
00:05:52,230 --> 00:05:53,870
So the patriarch made a suggestion

130
00:05:53,870 --> 00:05:56,070
and the three supervisors echoed his suggestion.

131
00:05:56,070 --> 00:05:58,270
They made new rules on the Dragon Boat Festival

132
00:05:58,270 --> 00:05:59,670
just to spare Cao Zhongda

133
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:01,670
from death.

134
00:06:02,030 --> 00:06:02,870
Therefore,

135
00:06:03,030 --> 00:06:03,950
Duobao's death

136
00:06:04,110 --> 00:06:05,750
has something to do

137
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:07,850
with Cao Zhongda and Cao Xiao.

138
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:18,990
What is on your mind?

139
00:06:20,590 --> 00:06:21,590
I'm just thinking

140
00:06:22,270 --> 00:06:23,230
if Cao Zhongda

141
00:06:23,370 --> 00:06:25,240
asked Cao Xiao to do those things.

142
00:06:28,070 --> 00:06:30,360
If we were not officials,

143
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:32,510
what would you want?

144
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:34,670
I would hope

145
00:06:35,870 --> 00:06:37,430
Cao Zhongda knows nothing

146
00:06:38,230 --> 00:06:40,070
and Cao Xiao acted on her own.

147
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:44,909
This case seems simple,

148
00:06:45,030 --> 00:06:46,680
but it's not that simple.

149
00:06:47,550 --> 00:06:49,590
We don't know

150
00:06:49,900 --> 00:06:51,659
if Cao Xiao knows

151
00:06:51,730 --> 00:06:53,420
about Duobao's background

152
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:55,730
or how much Mr. Cao knows about it.

153
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:58,260
So we can't act hastily

154
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,610
or jump to conclusions.

155
00:07:03,590 --> 00:07:04,390
You're right.

156
00:07:06,110 --> 00:07:06,710
I remember

157
00:07:06,710 --> 00:07:08,710
the owner of the ice cream shop is called...

158
00:07:08,710 --> 00:07:09,510
He Keke.

159
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:10,840
Let's go.

160
00:07:10,990 --> 00:07:12,850
Let's go to his shop to take a look.

161
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:14,990
Great minds think alike.

162
00:07:21,590 --> 00:07:23,350
[Xuesha Ice Cream Shop]

163
00:07:23,790 --> 00:07:24,160
Here.

164
00:07:24,630 --> 00:07:25,430
Please enjoy.

165
00:07:32,790 --> 00:07:34,190
I didn't know you'd come.

166
00:07:34,190 --> 00:07:35,390
I'm sorry for not welcoming you at the door.

167
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:37,250
Have a taste of today's ice cream.

168
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:41,790
After eating this delicious food at the banquet last night,

169
00:07:41,790 --> 00:07:44,670
I still couldn't forget its flavor after I went back.

170
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:46,390
I've wanted to eat it

171
00:07:46,510 --> 00:07:47,710
the whole day.

172
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:54,060
Your shop is the only one in Shazhou

173
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:56,150
that knows how to make ice cream, right?

174
00:07:56,150 --> 00:07:56,470
Yes.

175
00:07:56,870 --> 00:07:57,720
The only one.

176
00:07:58,670 --> 00:07:59,750
Did you deliver ice cream

177
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:01,350
to the Cao family yesterday?

178
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:02,510
No.

179
00:08:02,830 --> 00:08:04,270
We didn't deliver any to them.

180
00:08:04,270 --> 00:08:06,670
But Young Master Duobao came here to buy it.

181
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:07,820
Why didn't I know?

182
00:08:08,030 --> 00:08:08,390
Sir,

183
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:09,710
you went

184
00:08:09,710 --> 00:08:11,240
to Qiande Hall at that time.

185
00:08:16,430 --> 00:08:16,910
Hello.

186
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:18,350
Two portions of ice cream.

187
00:08:18,350 --> 00:08:19,150
To go, please.

188
00:08:19,470 --> 00:08:20,710
Young Master Duobao, you're here.

189
00:08:20,710 --> 00:08:21,670
My boss said

190
00:08:21,890 --> 00:08:23,240
you can have ice cream free of charge.

191
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,170
That's not okay.

192
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:26,190
I'm not going to buy it if you don't charge me any.

193
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:26,650
Well...

194
00:08:27,550 --> 00:08:28,590
This puts me in an awkward situation.

195
00:08:28,590 --> 00:08:29,960
You don't need to feel that way.

196
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,280
Just add more raisins

197
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:31,910
for me.

198
00:08:32,179 --> 00:08:33,909
If your boss asks,

199
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:34,960
just tell him

200
00:08:35,190 --> 00:08:36,340
you took the money,

201
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,909
but I didn't suffer losses.

202
00:08:37,909 --> 00:08:38,570
No problem.

203
00:08:39,150 --> 00:08:41,150
He bought two portions of ice cream?

204
00:08:41,260 --> 00:08:42,059
Are you sure?

205
00:08:42,350 --> 00:08:42,909
Yes.

206
00:08:43,070 --> 00:08:44,400
He did buy two portions.

207
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:48,560
My lords,

208
00:08:48,990 --> 00:08:50,850
I want to gossip about something.

209
00:08:51,150 --> 00:08:53,670
I went to congratulate Mr. Cao on his birthday today,

210
00:08:53,670 --> 00:08:55,510
but I saw Cao's Mansion has been sealed.

211
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:56,370
What happened?

212
00:08:56,390 --> 00:08:57,710
Since you know you're gossipy,

213
00:08:57,710 --> 00:08:58,310
don't ask.

214
00:08:59,190 --> 00:08:59,950
Mr. He.

215
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:02,140
Focus on your business.

216
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:03,630
This ice cream

217
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:05,270
really is delicious.

218
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,600
Maybe in 1,000 years,

219
00:09:07,630 --> 00:09:10,070
it will become a delicacy

220
00:09:10,090 --> 00:09:12,150
that everyone in this country likes.

221
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,840
Make me six more portions.

222
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,430
To go.

223
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:16,390
Okay.

224
00:09:24,710 --> 00:09:25,470
Ice cream?

225
00:09:26,590 --> 00:09:27,350
For me?

226
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:31,130
It's hot today.

227
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:33,200
It's for you to cool you off.

228
00:09:35,190 --> 00:09:36,590
I can't believe

229
00:09:36,950 --> 00:09:38,790
you're treating me, a prisoner, so well.

230
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:39,790
Mr. Cao,

231
00:09:41,030 --> 00:09:42,160
this is Qiande Hall,

232
00:09:42,190 --> 00:09:44,310
where you entertain guests.

233
00:09:44,340 --> 00:09:45,410
This is your place.

234
00:09:45,670 --> 00:09:47,080
I just asked you

235
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:48,470
to stay here alone for a few days.

236
00:09:48,470 --> 00:09:50,530
Why did you call yourself a prisoner?

237
00:09:51,830 --> 00:09:53,240
I'm a 60-year-old man

238
00:09:53,260 --> 00:09:54,530
who should have died.

239
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,510
No need to say that to comfort me.

240
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:00,470
Please.

241
00:10:01,620 --> 00:10:03,020
Ice cream is a good thing.

242
00:10:04,550 --> 00:10:05,550
It melts quickly.

243
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:06,280
So I

244
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:08,650
should eat it as soon as possible.

245
00:10:20,630 --> 00:10:23,060
Ice cream is my son's favorite.

246
00:10:27,190 --> 00:10:27,870
Can I

247
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:30,620
deliver this bowl to him?

248
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:37,040
I know Duobao

249
00:10:37,070 --> 00:10:38,510
is in Qiande Hall now.

250
00:10:39,750 --> 00:10:40,910
But the constables at the door

251
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:42,240
wouldn't let me see him.

252
00:10:46,870 --> 00:10:48,270
Since you're his mother,

253
00:10:48,860 --> 00:10:49,990
I'll take you there.

254
00:11:16,430 --> 00:11:17,150
My son.

255
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:21,800
This is all my fault.

256
00:11:22,310 --> 00:11:23,640
I was greedy for wealth.

257
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:25,580
I made you live in the Cao family

258
00:11:25,580 --> 00:11:27,880
and become their eyesore.

259
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:30,670
Who do you think in the Cao family

260
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:31,930
hates Duobao the most?

261
00:11:34,110 --> 00:11:35,510
Cao Rong and her husband,

262
00:11:36,390 --> 00:11:37,510
the murderers!

263
00:11:38,540 --> 00:11:39,390
Anyone else?

264
00:11:42,140 --> 00:11:42,910
Cao Xiao.

265
00:11:43,350 --> 00:11:44,880
She respects you very much.

266
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:45,510
She wouldn't even

267
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:46,790
speak ill of you.

268
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:49,610
Why do you think she hates Duobao?

269
00:11:50,190 --> 00:11:51,310
I was too greedy.

270
00:11:52,310 --> 00:11:55,150
I thought the Cao Family Cave is magnificent.

271
00:11:55,510 --> 00:11:57,710
So I wanted Ding Mao to be a provider too.

272
00:11:59,110 --> 00:12:00,970
Cao Zhongda agreed immediately.

273
00:12:01,230 --> 00:12:02,630
But since then,

274
00:12:03,020 --> 00:12:04,420
it feels like Cao Xiao

275
00:12:04,500 --> 00:12:06,100
has treated me differently.

276
00:12:08,430 --> 00:12:09,470
I always feel

277
00:12:09,490 --> 00:12:10,820
she's been watching me.

278
00:12:14,070 --> 00:12:14,710
That day,

279
00:12:15,950 --> 00:12:18,750
after Ding Mao found out about Cao Zhongda's will,

280
00:12:18,830 --> 00:12:20,540
he asked me to go to his room.

281
00:12:20,730 --> 00:12:21,830
50% for Duobao

282
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:23,650
and 10% for you.

283
00:12:24,230 --> 00:12:25,890
60% of the Cao family's assets

284
00:12:26,430 --> 00:12:28,020
will be ours soon.

285
00:12:29,150 --> 00:12:29,860
Our waiting

286
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:33,080
for the past 12 years is not in vain.

287
00:12:37,350 --> 00:12:38,080
Who's there?

288
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,230
I didn't clearly see

289
00:12:40,270 --> 00:12:41,470
who eavesdropped,

290
00:12:43,230 --> 00:12:43,910
but I think

291
00:12:44,900 --> 00:12:45,960
it must be Cao Xiao.

292
00:12:46,910 --> 00:12:48,370
That girl is very cunning.

293
00:12:48,460 --> 00:12:49,720
She seems to respect me

294
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:54,270
and be close to Duobao.

295
00:12:56,470 --> 00:12:57,390
In fact,

296
00:12:58,230 --> 00:12:59,260
she's always been on guard

297
00:12:59,260 --> 00:13:00,460
against me and my son.

298
00:13:09,350 --> 00:13:10,550
I don't eat ice cream.

299
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:12,910
You don't like it?

300
00:13:13,230 --> 00:13:14,980
I ate it once last year.

301
00:13:15,030 --> 00:13:16,290
Then I had diarrhoea.

302
00:13:16,310 --> 00:13:18,710
So my mother wouldn't let me eat it anymore.

303
00:13:21,270 --> 00:13:21,790
Sister,

304
00:13:21,990 --> 00:13:22,630
you eat.

305
00:13:23,030 --> 00:13:24,420
The ice cream won't taste good

306
00:13:24,420 --> 00:13:25,360
if it melts.

307
00:13:26,350 --> 00:13:27,750
You're such a sensible kid.

308
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:28,950
Actually, ice cream

309
00:13:28,990 --> 00:13:30,830
is my uncle's favorite.

310
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:33,720
He even wrote the methods of making ice cream

311
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:35,670
in his red-covered book.

312
00:13:37,470 --> 00:13:38,510
Who is the closest

313
00:13:38,530 --> 00:13:40,060
to your uncle in the family?

314
00:13:40,110 --> 00:13:40,590
Me.

315
00:13:41,230 --> 00:13:42,500
And Aunt Xiao.

316
00:13:42,700 --> 00:13:44,720
But she seems to have bickered

317
00:13:44,730 --> 00:13:45,790
with him recently.

318
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:48,140
I saw her stare at him secretly

319
00:13:48,190 --> 00:13:50,290
many times.

320
00:13:50,910 --> 00:13:52,240
She looked very fierce.

321
00:14:00,190 --> 00:14:01,390
It's almost melting.

322
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:04,030
You're a bad boy.

323
00:14:05,230 --> 00:14:06,270
I came all the way

324
00:14:06,270 --> 00:14:07,470
to deliver ice cream to you.

325
00:14:07,470 --> 00:14:09,530
I can't believe you said I'm a bad boy.

326
00:14:11,390 --> 00:14:12,470
Are you angry?

327
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:14,030
Boy,

328
00:14:14,350 --> 00:14:15,610
you don't understand.

329
00:14:15,870 --> 00:14:16,790
Bad

330
00:14:16,810 --> 00:14:17,550
doesn't necessarily

331
00:14:17,550 --> 00:14:19,030
mean evil.

332
00:14:19,630 --> 00:14:21,360
Take Fan, that old man, as an example.

333
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,550
When he was pursuing me,

334
00:14:22,550 --> 00:14:24,150
I always said he was a bad guy.

335
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:28,710
You're shy?

336
00:14:30,180 --> 00:14:32,110
Then you must like me.

337
00:14:33,950 --> 00:14:34,950
Take me with you.

338
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:37,390
I'll be nice to you forever.

339
00:14:37,950 --> 00:14:39,400
I don't want to die here.

340
00:14:39,430 --> 00:14:40,630
I want to live longer.

341
00:14:40,630 --> 00:14:41,350
Take me with you.

342
00:14:41,350 --> 00:14:42,080
How dare you!

343
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:52,470
Let me ask you.

344
00:14:53,230 --> 00:14:54,190
In this family,

345
00:14:54,830 --> 00:14:56,360
who treated Duobao the best

346
00:14:56,690 --> 00:14:58,350
and who treated him the worst?

347
00:14:59,110 --> 00:15:00,670
His mother treated him the best.

348
00:15:00,670 --> 00:15:02,410
My father treated him the worst.

349
00:15:02,410 --> 00:15:04,640
Are you saying Cao Zhongda

350
00:15:05,510 --> 00:15:06,770
treated Duobao badly?

351
00:15:07,310 --> 00:15:08,070
Of course.

352
00:15:08,230 --> 00:15:10,110
He treated us, his three daughters, much better.

353
00:15:10,110 --> 00:15:12,090
Duobao said he didn't want to do business.

354
00:15:12,090 --> 00:15:13,000
He always said

355
00:15:13,030 --> 00:15:14,310
he wanted to become a broker.

356
00:15:14,310 --> 00:15:16,370
So my father almost beat him to death.

357
00:15:17,160 --> 00:15:17,730
Stop.

358
00:15:17,870 --> 00:15:18,670
-No.
-Father.

359
00:15:20,130 --> 00:15:21,340
-Stop, Father.
-No!

360
00:15:21,510 --> 00:15:21,970
Father.

361
00:15:22,990 --> 00:15:23,350
I...

362
00:15:27,410 --> 00:15:28,870
Get out of my way, Ding Mao!

363
00:15:29,510 --> 00:15:30,070
Mr. Cao,

364
00:15:30,910 --> 00:15:32,170
please don't be angry.

365
00:15:32,260 --> 00:15:33,660
If you beat him this hard,

366
00:15:33,950 --> 00:15:35,310
you'll beat him to death.

367
00:15:35,310 --> 00:15:36,710
I'm disciplining my son.

368
00:15:36,750 --> 00:15:37,430
Get out of my way!

369
00:15:37,430 --> 00:15:37,830
Move!

370
00:15:37,850 --> 00:15:38,820
Please.

371
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:41,620
At that time, I thought

372
00:15:43,910 --> 00:15:45,150
I was very lucky

373
00:15:46,260 --> 00:15:47,430
to be his daughter.

374
00:15:48,470 --> 00:15:49,270
To be honest,

375
00:15:49,790 --> 00:15:51,590
it's good enough

376
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:54,150
that I can get 10% of the family assets.

377
00:15:54,150 --> 00:15:55,790
If I'm not greedy,

378
00:15:56,430 --> 00:15:57,630
the assets are enough

379
00:15:57,960 --> 00:16:00,020
for me to spend for the rest of my life.

380
00:16:16,190 --> 00:16:17,470
Why have you stopped eating?

381
00:16:17,470 --> 00:16:18,070
It's cold.

382
00:16:18,990 --> 00:16:21,720
No matter how delicious it is, I can't eat too much.

383
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:22,110
Yes.

384
00:16:22,910 --> 00:16:24,590
There is something I don't understand.

385
00:16:24,590 --> 00:16:26,390
Could you please enlighten me?

386
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:27,400
Go ahead.

387
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,790
Since you have caught the murderer,

388
00:16:29,790 --> 00:16:31,450
why did you ask my whole family

389
00:16:31,470 --> 00:16:32,840
to live in Qiande Hall?

390
00:16:34,190 --> 00:16:35,660
My daughter, Saisai, is still a little girl.

391
00:16:35,660 --> 00:16:37,750
But she was forced to separate from her mother.

392
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:39,210
Who came up with this idea?

393
00:16:39,490 --> 00:16:40,630
My husband, Li Chi,

394
00:16:40,670 --> 00:16:41,990
was just thoughtless at that time.

395
00:16:41,990 --> 00:16:43,390
He didn't commit murder.

396
00:16:43,790 --> 00:16:44,390
Under which rule

397
00:16:44,390 --> 00:16:45,530
did the state government

398
00:16:45,530 --> 00:16:46,530
put him in prison?

399
00:16:46,630 --> 00:16:47,110
And...

400
00:17:10,190 --> 00:17:11,450
You still won't eat it?

401
00:17:14,150 --> 00:17:16,079
I like ice cream with more raisins.

402
00:17:16,540 --> 00:17:18,270
This kind of ordinary ice cream

403
00:17:18,470 --> 00:17:19,579
is not delicious.

404
00:17:20,990 --> 00:17:22,150
More raisins?

405
00:17:22,829 --> 00:17:24,410
Last night, Duobao brought two portions of ice cream

406
00:17:24,410 --> 00:17:25,869
with more raisins home.

407
00:17:26,310 --> 00:17:27,190
One portion

408
00:17:28,270 --> 00:17:29,230
was for me.

409
00:17:29,830 --> 00:17:31,430
Duobao knew best what I like.

410
00:17:32,710 --> 00:17:33,970
I enjoyed the ice cream

411
00:17:34,870 --> 00:17:36,430
very much.

412
00:17:46,830 --> 00:17:47,430
Who is it?

413
00:17:48,510 --> 00:17:49,270
Sister Xiao,

414
00:17:49,420 --> 00:17:50,640
can I come in?

415
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:52,830
Come in.

416
00:18:00,350 --> 00:18:01,080
Sister Xiao.

417
00:18:02,190 --> 00:18:03,950
I brought you ice cream.

418
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,090
Who wants it?

419
00:18:05,230 --> 00:18:05,960
Take it away.

420
00:18:08,590 --> 00:18:10,790
You've always been mean to me recently.

421
00:18:11,030 --> 00:18:13,030
Did I do something to make you angry?

422
00:18:14,910 --> 00:18:17,540
I know our father's 60th birthday funeral is approaching.

423
00:18:17,540 --> 00:18:18,970
You are sad.

424
00:18:19,070 --> 00:18:20,830
I feel sad too.

425
00:18:21,230 --> 00:18:23,030
But we should get over it

426
00:18:23,390 --> 00:18:24,650
and look to the future.

427
00:18:25,590 --> 00:18:26,920
Have some ice cream now.

428
00:18:27,070 --> 00:18:28,520
I asked them to add more raisins.

429
00:18:28,520 --> 00:18:29,710
I know you like it.

430
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,000
One is not enough.

431
00:18:32,630 --> 00:18:33,690
I want both of them.

432
00:18:38,130 --> 00:18:39,860
Then I'll put both of them here.

433
00:18:40,150 --> 00:18:41,310
Eat them as soon as possible.

434
00:18:41,310 --> 00:18:42,440
Don't let them melt.

435
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:49,160
Duobao was a good kid.

436
00:18:50,110 --> 00:18:50,640
But he...

437
00:18:52,670 --> 00:18:54,440
You were an important official in Chang'an

438
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:56,080
and investigated countless mysterious cases.

439
00:18:56,080 --> 00:18:57,340
You must have found out

440
00:18:58,910 --> 00:19:00,570
Duobao's background, right?

441
00:19:03,910 --> 00:19:05,570
It's a disgrace to our family.

442
00:19:06,150 --> 00:19:07,610
I'm not going to repeat it.

443
00:19:08,230 --> 00:19:09,490
I bribed the patriarch

444
00:19:10,430 --> 00:19:13,110
and the members of the Family Supervisory Committee.

445
00:19:13,110 --> 00:19:14,310
I prepared the poison

446
00:19:15,630 --> 00:19:17,190
just to poison Duobao

447
00:19:17,830 --> 00:19:19,360
on the Dragon Boat Festival

448
00:19:19,630 --> 00:19:21,090
so that my father can live.

449
00:19:22,110 --> 00:19:22,750
So

450
00:19:42,670 --> 00:19:43,930
I caught up with Duobao

451
00:19:44,710 --> 00:19:45,390
and told him

452
00:19:45,810 --> 00:19:48,210
I couldn't finish two portions of ice cream

453
00:19:48,310 --> 00:19:49,570
and I was just kidding.

454
00:19:50,910 --> 00:19:51,570
Therefore,

455
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:52,640
after you found out

456
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:54,400
Fan Songling strangled Duobao to death,

457
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:55,230
I immediately took back

458
00:19:55,230 --> 00:19:56,250
Duobao's body, put him in a coffin,

459
00:19:56,250 --> 00:19:57,110
and buried him.

460
00:19:57,630 --> 00:19:58,340
That was because I didn't want you

461
00:19:58,340 --> 00:20:00,070
to continue to investigate it.

462
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:02,910
I did everything on my own.

463
00:20:03,020 --> 00:20:04,500
I violated the Cao family's rules.

464
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:05,950
I'm too ashamed to face my father.

465
00:20:05,950 --> 00:20:06,950
Execute me!

466
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:15,270
Ice cream really is a good thing.

467
00:20:16,430 --> 00:20:18,070
I just hope ice cream

468
00:20:18,580 --> 00:20:20,240
can be remembered by tourists

469
00:20:20,630 --> 00:20:22,350
so that they'll come to Shazhou again.

470
00:20:22,350 --> 00:20:23,790
Only the prosperity of trade and travel

471
00:20:23,790 --> 00:20:25,200
can make Shazhou flourishing.

472
00:20:25,200 --> 00:20:26,310
Then the people

473
00:20:26,550 --> 00:20:27,910
can live better lives.

474
00:20:28,750 --> 00:20:29,680
Unfortunately,

475
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:31,340
my time has come.

476
00:20:32,710 --> 00:20:34,170
I can't make it to that day.

477
00:20:35,010 --> 00:20:35,760
Mr. Cao,

478
00:20:36,310 --> 00:20:37,390
you're no longer restricted

479
00:20:37,390 --> 00:20:38,960
by the Family Supervisory Committee's rules.

480
00:20:38,960 --> 00:20:40,820
Why did you say your time has come?

481
00:20:41,550 --> 00:20:43,310
Fate has the final say.

482
00:20:44,430 --> 00:20:46,070
I tried so hard

483
00:20:46,440 --> 00:20:48,030
to avoid my 60th birthday funeral.

484
00:20:48,030 --> 00:20:49,310
But unexpectedly,

485
00:20:50,820 --> 00:20:53,190
Detective Di's disciple came to Shazhou.

486
00:20:54,390 --> 00:20:55,070
Alright.

487
00:20:56,270 --> 00:20:57,440
You let me

488
00:20:58,030 --> 00:20:59,670
plead guilty in Qiande Hall.

489
00:21:00,130 --> 00:21:02,460
You've protected my dignity well enough.

490
00:21:07,710 --> 00:21:08,670
Plead guilty?

491
00:21:09,390 --> 00:21:09,870
Yes.

492
00:21:11,710 --> 00:21:12,470
I

493
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:15,190
didn't want to die.

494
00:21:15,350 --> 00:21:17,480
I poisoned Duobao in order to survive.

495
00:21:17,550 --> 00:21:19,360
I committed a heinous crime.

496
00:21:19,510 --> 00:21:20,710
It's against ethics.

497
00:21:21,270 --> 00:21:23,070
I'm too ashamed to face my family

498
00:21:23,620 --> 00:21:25,790
or the people of Shazhou.

499
00:21:26,710 --> 00:21:28,470
I wish to die as soon as possible.

500
00:21:28,470 --> 00:21:29,670
Please grant my wish.

501
00:21:33,340 --> 00:21:35,970
[Qiande Hall]

502
00:21:57,950 --> 00:22:00,870
Mr. Cao and Cao Xiao pled guilty at the same time.

503
00:22:01,150 --> 00:22:02,800
We found red aconite

504
00:22:02,950 --> 00:22:04,550
in Cao Xiao's room.

505
00:22:05,830 --> 00:22:07,830
But Mr. Cao doesn't have the poison.

506
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:09,800
Who said he doesn't have it?

507
00:22:11,990 --> 00:22:13,350
The poison in Duobao's body

508
00:22:13,350 --> 00:22:14,830
is a kind of aconite.

509
00:22:14,860 --> 00:22:16,320
It's commonly known as...

510
00:22:16,590 --> 00:22:17,510
"Red Neck".

511
00:22:20,030 --> 00:22:21,090
Are you surprised?

512
00:22:21,330 --> 00:22:22,830
I poisoned him myself.

513
00:22:23,110 --> 00:22:24,750
Of course I know what it is.

514
00:22:25,350 --> 00:22:25,950
Mr. Cao,

515
00:22:26,460 --> 00:22:28,850
we have found this poison

516
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:30,200
in Cao Xiao's room.

517
00:22:30,230 --> 00:22:32,630
Does it necessarily mean she poisoned him?

518
00:22:32,870 --> 00:22:33,650
Listen.

519
00:22:33,830 --> 00:22:35,950
Xiao is a kind girl.

520
00:22:36,510 --> 00:22:38,310
She and Duobao were the closest.

521
00:22:38,340 --> 00:22:40,270
It's impossible that she poisoned him.

522
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:41,330
Xiao is benevolent,

523
00:22:41,330 --> 00:22:42,030
filial,

524
00:22:42,310 --> 00:22:43,400
and very smart.

525
00:22:43,470 --> 00:22:45,070
She's very good at doing business.

526
00:22:45,070 --> 00:22:46,590
Although she is a girl,

527
00:22:47,390 --> 00:22:48,270
she is outstanding

528
00:22:48,270 --> 00:22:49,950
among the descendants of the Cao family.

529
00:22:49,950 --> 00:22:52,500
She is also the future and hope of Tang.

530
00:22:53,430 --> 00:22:54,260
I also know

531
00:22:54,430 --> 00:22:55,960
your master, Detective Di,

532
00:22:57,430 --> 00:22:59,160
was very good at solving cases.

533
00:22:59,430 --> 00:23:01,030
But he loved the people more.

534
00:23:01,990 --> 00:23:03,430
If you suspect Xiao,

535
00:23:03,790 --> 00:23:06,050
you'll be disrespectful to your master.

536
00:23:06,710 --> 00:23:07,510
Wait a minute.

537
00:23:29,350 --> 00:23:30,830
Guys, step aside.

538
00:23:30,950 --> 00:23:31,950
Let me take a look.

539
00:23:39,950 --> 00:23:41,150
It's really Red Neck.

540
00:23:41,710 --> 00:23:43,910
Both of them claimed to be the murderer.

541
00:23:44,870 --> 00:23:46,470
Did they conspire with each other?

542
00:23:46,470 --> 00:23:47,070
-No.
-No.

543
00:23:48,430 --> 00:23:49,160
You go ahead.

544
00:23:49,710 --> 00:23:50,770
If they conspired,

545
00:23:51,110 --> 00:23:52,550
they would have discussed in advance.

546
00:23:52,550 --> 00:23:53,630
After poisoning him,

547
00:23:53,630 --> 00:23:55,360
they should have destroyed the evidence immediately.

548
00:23:55,360 --> 00:23:56,070
They wouldn't have let us

549
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:57,930
find these two packets of poison.

550
00:23:59,300 --> 00:24:01,320
If they didn't conspire,

551
00:24:01,800 --> 00:24:03,850
who is the murderer?

552
00:24:05,220 --> 00:24:06,430
How about this?

553
00:24:07,230 --> 00:24:08,910
If you think Mr. Cao is the murderer,

554
00:24:08,910 --> 00:24:09,570
stand here.

555
00:24:10,110 --> 00:24:11,750
If you think Cao Xiao is the murderer,

556
00:24:11,750 --> 00:24:12,750
stand over there.

557
00:24:12,870 --> 00:24:13,630
Good idea.

558
00:24:21,390 --> 00:24:21,910
You two,

559
00:24:21,990 --> 00:24:22,990
choose your side.

560
00:24:29,910 --> 00:24:31,170
I haven't decided yet.

561
00:24:40,390 --> 00:24:41,150
Me neither.

562
00:24:42,980 --> 00:24:43,840
How about this?

563
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:46,500
You guys tell us your own reasons first.

564
00:24:47,110 --> 00:24:47,550
Xijun,

565
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:48,760
you first.

566
00:24:49,310 --> 00:24:50,640
Cao Xiao has the poison.

567
00:24:50,910 --> 00:24:52,190
The motive

568
00:24:52,390 --> 00:24:53,230
and the timing of the murder

569
00:24:53,230 --> 00:24:54,070
both match up.

570
00:24:54,590 --> 00:24:55,720
We also found plants

571
00:24:55,990 --> 00:24:56,870
used as decorations

572
00:24:56,870 --> 00:24:58,720
for ice cream in her room.

573
00:24:59,190 --> 00:24:59,650
It shows

574
00:25:00,110 --> 00:25:01,440
her confession is true.

575
00:25:02,470 --> 00:25:04,000
Xijun is sober-minded

576
00:25:04,070 --> 00:25:06,230
and meticulous.

577
00:25:06,250 --> 00:25:07,740
I don't think so.

578
00:25:08,190 --> 00:25:09,520
When I entered Shazhou,

579
00:25:09,630 --> 00:25:11,560
I thought Mr. Cao was a kind person.

580
00:25:11,990 --> 00:25:13,520
So I wanted to befriend him.

581
00:25:14,310 --> 00:25:16,030
From last night's banquet

