to take the blame.

865
00:37:18,190 --> 00:37:20,320
Now it's difficult to solve this case.

866
00:37:20,450 --> 00:37:21,850
You don't believe

867
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:23,840
Cao Zhongda poisoned him?

868
00:37:24,910 --> 00:37:26,570
Human nature is complicated,

869
00:37:26,950 --> 00:37:27,430
but I'm

870
00:37:27,790 --> 00:37:30,520
more inclined to believe Cao Xiao is the murderer.

871
00:37:30,520 --> 00:37:32,350
If Cao Zhongda is not the murderer,

872
00:37:32,350 --> 00:37:33,550
how did he know

873
00:37:33,730 --> 00:37:36,010
it was the ice cream that poisoned Duobao

874
00:37:36,030 --> 00:37:37,630
instead of something else

875
00:37:37,790 --> 00:37:39,700
like water or tea?

876
00:37:41,670 --> 00:37:42,870
At first,

877
00:37:43,310 --> 00:37:45,030
I didn't suspect Mr. Cao.

878
00:37:45,610 --> 00:37:47,400
But he accurately

879
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:49,230
identified the poisonous ice cream.

880
00:37:49,230 --> 00:37:50,230
This alone

881
00:37:50,460 --> 00:37:51,870
can't prove

882
00:37:51,870 --> 00:37:53,070
Mr. Cao is the one who poisoned Duobao.

883
00:37:53,070 --> 00:37:53,710
I think

884
00:37:54,020 --> 00:37:55,110
it's more likely that he wants

885
00:37:55,110 --> 00:37:56,770
to take the blame for Cao Xiao.

886
00:37:58,670 --> 00:38:00,030
Although we know this,

887
00:38:00,150 --> 00:38:01,080
there is nothing

888
00:38:01,630 --> 00:38:02,790
we can do about it.

889
00:38:13,910 --> 00:38:16,110
You and I are not officials of this city.

890
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,800
We came to Shazhou as guests.

891
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:20,340
Mr. Cao showed us warm hospitality.

892
00:38:20,340 --> 00:38:22,370
But now he has become a murderer.

893
00:38:23,990 --> 00:38:26,190
Since he's determined to plead guilty,

894
00:38:26,350 --> 00:38:27,210
why don't we...

895
00:38:28,430 --> 00:38:30,150
do him a favor?

896
00:38:32,150 --> 00:38:33,080
What do you mean?

897
00:38:44,760 --> 00:38:45,750
I've pled guilty.

898
00:38:45,750 --> 00:38:47,510
Is it still necessary to interrogate me?

899
00:38:47,510 --> 00:38:48,630
It's late. I'm going to sleep.

900
00:38:48,630 --> 00:38:49,230
Get out.

901
00:38:49,910 --> 00:38:51,510
The poisoner has confessed.

902
00:38:51,940 --> 00:38:53,830
So you don't need to take the blame for him.

903
00:38:53,830 --> 00:38:54,310
Leave.

904
00:38:54,550 --> 00:38:55,780
This is not a prison.

905
00:38:56,110 --> 00:38:57,200
No one can imprison

906
00:38:57,230 --> 00:38:58,230
innocent people.

907
00:38:58,910 --> 00:38:59,910
Go home.

908
00:39:00,210 --> 00:39:01,670
The Cao family's business

909
00:39:01,670 --> 00:39:03,590
depends on you in the future.

910
00:39:03,620 --> 00:39:04,510
I told you

911
00:39:04,620 --> 00:39:05,660
I poisoned him!

912
00:39:05,690 --> 00:39:06,350
Cao Xiao!

913
00:39:08,520 --> 00:39:10,950
This is a crime that will cost you your life.

914
00:39:11,430 --> 00:39:12,870
You are still young.

915
00:39:13,150 --> 00:39:14,430
Why are you acting tough?

916
00:39:14,430 --> 00:39:16,290
Do you think you're being filial?

917
00:39:16,910 --> 00:39:19,590
How can Mr. Cao

918
00:39:19,870 --> 00:39:21,580
bear to live

919
00:39:22,220 --> 00:39:23,440
after watching you

920
00:39:23,470 --> 00:39:25,950
die for him?

921
00:39:32,750 --> 00:39:33,230
Father.

922
00:39:34,750 --> 00:39:35,550
Father.

923
00:39:38,650 --> 00:39:39,910
I got you into trouble.

924
00:39:41,890 --> 00:39:43,730
It's my fault.

925
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:45,180
What?

926
00:39:45,870 --> 00:39:48,600
Did you and your father conspire with each other?

927
00:39:49,710 --> 00:39:50,880
My father didn't know

928
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:52,790
about Duobao's background at all.

929
00:39:52,790 --> 00:39:53,870
I told him

930
00:39:53,870 --> 00:39:54,910
about my plan.

931
00:39:58,270 --> 00:39:59,200
What did you say?

932
00:40:00,070 --> 00:40:00,600
Foolish!

933
00:40:01,350 --> 00:40:02,500
I've taught you

934
00:40:02,780 --> 00:40:03,710
how to study,

935
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:04,950
how to be a righteous person,

936
00:40:04,950 --> 00:40:06,700
and how to do business since you were little.

937
00:40:06,700 --> 00:40:07,990
What have you learned?

938
00:40:08,670 --> 00:40:10,250
My daughter

939
00:40:10,470 --> 00:40:12,070
wants to kill someone.

940
00:40:12,380 --> 00:40:12,900
Father,

941
00:40:15,070 --> 00:40:16,270
I'm sorry.

942
00:40:17,120 --> 00:40:17,970
But this matter...

943
00:40:17,970 --> 00:40:18,570
Listen.

944
00:40:19,190 --> 00:40:19,920
Just pretend

945
00:40:20,670 --> 00:40:22,530
that you know nothing about this.

946
00:40:22,830 --> 00:40:24,430
Just focus on your business.

947
00:40:25,350 --> 00:40:26,900
Marry into a good family

948
00:40:27,270 --> 00:40:29,270
and live a simple life in the future.

949
00:40:29,910 --> 00:40:31,020
Remember,

950
00:40:31,670 --> 00:40:33,270
you must do as many good deeds

951
00:40:33,350 --> 00:40:35,350
as you can in this life.

952
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:37,680
Father is very kind.

953
00:40:39,790 --> 00:40:41,350
But I just couldn't stand by

954
00:40:41,350 --> 00:40:42,480
and let Ye Lai and Ding Mao's plot

955
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:43,510
succeed.

956
00:40:44,030 --> 00:40:45,890
I couldn't bear to see my father

957
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:47,430
go to his 60th birthday funeral either.

958
00:40:47,430 --> 00:40:48,710
So I decided

959
00:40:49,990 --> 00:40:51,450
to do everything on my own.

960
00:40:53,390 --> 00:40:54,510
But in the end...

961
00:41:25,030 --> 00:41:25,670
Who is it?

962
00:41:26,270 --> 00:41:27,020
Sister Xiao,

963
00:41:27,310 --> 00:41:28,380
can I come in?

964
00:41:30,750 --> 00:41:31,230
Come in.

965
00:41:31,670 --> 00:41:33,350
I brought you ice cream.

966
00:41:34,190 --> 00:41:35,190
Who wants it?

967
00:41:35,210 --> 00:41:35,940
Take it away.

968
00:41:36,550 --> 00:41:38,750
You've always been mean to me recently.

969
00:41:39,070 --> 00:41:41,070
Did I do something to make you angry?

970
00:41:43,550 --> 00:41:46,340
I know our father's 60th birthday funeral is approaching.

971
00:41:46,340 --> 00:41:47,630
You are sad.

972
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:49,580
I feel sad too.

973
00:41:49,990 --> 00:41:51,800
But we should get over it

974
00:41:52,070 --> 00:41:53,330
and look to the future.

975
00:41:54,270 --> 00:41:55,600
Have some ice cream now.

976
00:41:55,790 --> 00:41:57,470
I asked them to add more raisins.

977
00:41:57,470 --> 00:41:58,550
I know you like it.

978
00:42:05,710 --> 00:42:06,510
So,

979
00:42:06,910 --> 00:42:08,170
you didn't poison him.

980
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:13,800
My father poisoned him,

981
00:42:14,190 --> 00:42:15,520
but if it weren't for me,

982
00:42:16,490 --> 00:42:18,420
he wouldn't have done that.

983
00:42:19,150 --> 00:42:20,900
If my father is sentenced to death,

984
00:42:20,900 --> 00:42:23,050
I will die with him.

985
00:42:23,480 --> 00:42:26,080
Who told you it was Mr. Cao who poisoned Duobao?

986
00:42:29,460 --> 00:42:30,310
My father didn't do it?

987
00:42:30,310 --> 00:42:31,170
Then who did it?

988
00:42:31,590 --> 00:42:33,700
Cao Xiao,

989
00:42:33,870 --> 00:42:35,350
you think you are smart.

990
00:42:35,380 --> 00:42:36,710
You're self-righteous.

991
00:42:36,710 --> 00:42:37,310
You think

992
00:42:37,310 --> 00:42:39,570
you are taking the blame for your father.

993
00:42:39,630 --> 00:42:41,950
But you almost helped the real murderer

994
00:42:42,830 --> 00:42:44,510
get away with it.
